Author: Sounkou Mahamane Toure [aut, cre],
  Kenichi Yasukata [cph] (fmalloc),
  Wolfram Gloger [cph] (ptmalloc3),
  Free Software Foundation, Inc. [cph] (selected GNU C Library support files)
Maintainer: Sounkou Mahamane Toure <sounkoutoure@gmail.com>
Description: Provides experimental memory-mapped file allocation capabilities for R using
    the 'fmalloc' library. The package exposes ALTREP, file-backed vector
    allocation for logical, integer, numeric, raw, complex, character, and list
    vectors, plus explicit runtime handles for working with multiple backing files in one R
    process.
